    <body>
        <pb n="4"/>
        <p n="7">
            <ln n="1"/>can come you will have received
            <ln n="2"/>a telegram from me before you get
            <ln n="3"/>this letter. I think she is bring another <!-- seb:added a missing word "she" -->
            <ln n="4"/>boy and another girl with her. Do 
            <ln n="5"/>you think we can find room for all?
        </p>
        <p n="8">
            <ln n="1"/>I received the map and tickets <!-- seb:fixed typo in received -->
            <ln n="2"/>O.K. Someone very thoughtfully mark- <!-- seb: i think "may" might be "very" -->
<!--em: resolved the previous comment-->
            <ln n="3"/>ed the rest <unclear reason="write???">wrote</unclear> in red pencil. Wish <!-- seb: i think "rest" could be "best" -->
            <!--em: resolved the previous comment-->
            <ln n="4"/>I knew who it was so that I could thank
            <ln n="5"/>them.
        </p>
        <p n="9">
            <ln n="1"/>Don't get me any<crossOut>n</crossOut> more things
            <ln n="2"/>for X mas. Give it to <organization>the Red Cross</organization>
            <ln n="3"/>or the <organization>Near East Relief</organization> or something.
            <ln n="4"/>You do too much for <crossOut>me</crossOut>.
        </p>
        <closer>
            <ln n="1"/>Much love,
            <ln n="2"/>Warren.
        </closer>
    </body>
